channel.title: My RuneScape Goals
channel.description:
Hey MoparScape,
My Goal is to get 80 or higher in every skill on RuneScape. Then after that I'm going to be doing all of the intermediate quests I can then all of the hard ones and continue along those lines. I'm doing it all legit, and only playing 2 hours before school and 2-3 hours after school. So in total 4-5 hours a day. The skills left are the ones that cost the most money, or take the longest to do. I want to get 80 in all of my skills so that I can start playing and having more fun, In the game.
Here are my Skills;
[i]Note: I will be posting an update of my Skills every 2 days, so you can see my progress. They will be updated in this post.[/i]

Two hours before school, what time do you get up?
I get up at 5:00 AM, Train until 7-8 am, then go to school. But if I don't train then I still get up at 5:00 am do my weights and fitness until 6, then play till 7:30.

I’m currently 24k experience until 79 farming which is when I’ll be 2,200 in total level. After 80 farming, I’ll be working on 80 Constuction. Then I’ll be working on 80 Slayer, After that I will try and get 80 summoning.
